   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="abstract" resp="kg">
            <p>
               <rs type="event" ref="ev__SB_CD_00685"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__johann_waitz_QGW_II_II_3263">Hanns Waicz, der <roleName type="prof"
                           >kürsner</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"
                           >mitburger</roleName> zu Wienn</rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">beurkundet, dass</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="event" ref="ev__SB_CD_00685_men_1">ihm seine Hausfrau Kathrei, Mathesen
                     Lanczenperger, des schuster seligen, tochter, 100 lb dn. zu rechter haimsteur
                     zugebracht, er ihr dagegen 200 lb dn. zu rechter morgengab versprochen
                     habe,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">und verschreibt</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__katharina_QGW_II_II_3459">ihr</rs></rs> dafür <rs type="fn"
                     role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">mit Handen</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__oswald_reicholf_QGW_II_II_3314"><roleName
                           type="title">hern</roleName> Oswalts Reicholf, <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien">burgermaister</roleName></rs>, und <rs type="org"
                        ref="org__wien">des Rathes</rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place"
                        ref="pl__wien-immo_hoher_markt_4"><roleName type="owner"
                           corresp="pe__johann_waitz_QGW_II_II_3263">sein</roleName> Haus, <roleName
                           type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-hoher_markt">gelegen am
                           Hohenmarkcht</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-hoher_markt_wentkremen">undern
                           Wenndtkremen oben am egk</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-kramhof">in dem Kramhof</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-perkhof">zenagst dem Perkchhof an
                           aim tail</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_hoher_markt_3">und an dem
                           andern zenagst</roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_hoher_markt_3"><roleName type="owner"
                              corresp="pe__johann_payr_QGW_II_II_3263">Hannsen Payr, des
                              schuster,</roleName> haus</rs></rs></rs> .</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="seal">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__SB_CD_00685"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit <rs
                        type="org" ref="org__wien">dem städtischen Grundsiegel</rs> und dem Siegel
                     des <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_renhart_QGW_II_II_3282">Wiener <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">Bürgers</roleName> Niclas
                        Renhart</rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="nota">
            <p>Indorsat: Hannsen Waiczen, kursner, haimsteur- und morgengab- brief seiner hausfraun
               Kathrein, Mathesen Lanczenperger, des schuster seligen, tochter, uber IIIc tl. dn .
            </p>
         </div>
